rows.label: qst720502_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, I can see the bridge.
That must be Lett Bridge.

rows.label: qst720502_msg0004
rows.name:
You think so?
They don't look like much to me.

rows.label: qst720502_msg0005
rows.name:
Whatever you think, people will be in
trouble if they can't cross the bridge.
We have to deal with this now.

rows.label: qst720502_msg0006
rows.name: Don't let your guard down, everyone!
